was actually used in

38:52.486 --> 38:53.453
<i>The Empire Strikes Back.</i>

38:53.487 --> 38:55.422
Really?
[Laughs]

38:55.456 --> 38:57.490
Get out of here, it was an <i> Empire?</i>

38:57.525 --> 39:00.627
- Guess who's saber.
- Gotta be Luke's.

39:00.662 --> 39:01.628
Yep, Luke's.

39:01.663 --> 39:03.030
It was...exciting.

39:03.064 --> 39:04.832
I mean, it really was
because you're seeing

39:04.866 --> 39:07.001
